{"article_id":"oZU6bj5ueF36ldkU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump ' s top economic adviser Larry Kudlow said Sunday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he expected China to retaliate against the administration ' s planned tariff hike .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"\" I think","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"I do ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"but","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"it ' s interesting ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"the expected countermeasures haven ' t yet materialized , \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Kudlow told Chris Wallace on \" Fox News Sunday.","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" \" I reckon","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"they will .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"We ' ll see what they come up with .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"So far we haven ' t heard on that basis . \"","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Talks with the Chinese are in limbo","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"as the Chinese delegation left D.C. without an inked trade deal earlier this week .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"Kudlow said","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"new talks haven ' t been scheduled yet ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"but the Chinese have invited Amb . Robert Lighthizer , the U.S. trade representative , to Beijing .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"He added","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that it ' s likely Trump and Chinese President Xi Jinping will meet at next month ' s G20 in Japan .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Last Sunday , Trump used Twitter","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"to announce the tariff spike .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"\" For 10 months , China has been paying Tariffs to the USA of 25 % on 50 Billion Dollars of High Tech , and 10 % on 200 Billions Dollars of other goods .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"These payments are partially responsible for our great economic results .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"The 10 % will go up to 25 % on Friday , \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"\" 325 Billion Dollars of additional goods","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"sent to us by China ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"but remain untaxed ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"but will be shortly , at a rate of 25 % . \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Trump complained","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"that the trade talks with China were moving too slowly ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"as the country tried to renegotiate portions of the deal .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"This Sunday , Kudlow said","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"the U.S. had started the process","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"to increase these tariffs ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"but the full implementation could take months .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"\" We will have announcements ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"we will have hearings ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"we will have public comments , \"","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Kudlow explained .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"\" It could be a couple of months thereabouts . \"","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"While Wallace pointed out","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"that tariffs get passed along to the U.S. consumer ,","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Kudlow argued","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that China will be hurt too","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"thanks to the \" diminishing export market . \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"\" You ' ve got ta do what you ' ve got ta do .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"We ' ve had unfair trading practices all these years .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"And so in my judgment , the economic consequences are so small ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"but the possible improvement in trade and exports and open markets to the United States , this is worthwhile doing , \"","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"he said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":101,"left":69,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":62,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":52,"right":61,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclea